{"tid":1923459,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大教職員丈夫確診新冠肺炎　3名文學院教職員須檢疫","createTime":"2020-03-13T05:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T06:08:06.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc832365035360d8f58318558f3eaf1b35a81959","tid":1923459,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T05:39:15.000Z","msg":"香港大學今（13日）向教職員發電郵，指出港大醫療保健處昨晚（12日）接獲衛生防護中心通知，一名確診感染新型冠狀病毒肺炎男患者為該校教職員的配偶；該患者3月11日曾到大學診所求醫，當時有戴口罩，並被要求使用酒精搓手液及量體溫，而所有靠近他的工作人員都已穿著適當防護衣物。據了解，該名確診者是港大一名教職員的丈夫。<br />\n<br />\n港大在電郵指出，共有3名文學院教職員被列為密切接觸者，包括該名確診者的妻子，他們已到政府指定的檢疫中心隔離，全部暫未出現病徵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200313/s00001/1584074396959/%e6%b8%af%e5%a4%a7%e6%95%99%e8%81%b7%e5%93%a1%e4%b8%88%e5%a4%ab%e7%a2%ba%e8%a8%ba%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-3%e5%90%8d%e6%96%87%e5%ad%b8%e9%99%a2%e6%95%99%e8%81%b7%e5%93%a1%e9%a0%88%e6%aa%a2%e7%96%ab\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200313%2Fs00001%2F1584074396959%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2581%25b7%25e5%2593%25a1%25e4%25b8%2588%25e5%25a4%25ab%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e8%25a8%25ba%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-3%25e5%2590%258d%25e6%2596%2587%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e9%2599%25a2%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2581%25b7%25e5%2593%25a1%25e9%25a0%2588%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e7%2596%25ab&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCfulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=64dd9ac6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200313%2Fs00001%2F1584074396959%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2581%25b7%25e5%2593%25a1%25e4%25b8%2588%25e5%25a4%25ab%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e8%25a8%25ba%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-3%25e5%2590%258d%25e6%2596%2587%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e9%2599%25a2%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2581%25b7%25e5%2593%25a1%25e9%25a0%2588%25e6%25aa%25a2%